item.title: Hybrid pvp
item.dc:creator: @purestmage74 purestmage74
item.description:
@purestmage74 wrote:

First off, you can’t give rep with out yourself having at least 15+ rep.

Second of all, you can get your server on Google by simply just creating things on websites and publishing them with your servers name in the file title, or image title.

Like our server, “Elite Demons” i didn’t pay to be submitted on Google, guess they send out “robots & spiders” to your website, and just collect information from you.

But yea, id suggest something other than Hybrid PVP, if you’re considering hosting, there’s shit tons of hybrid pvp’s out there.

Try to code on them though yea, easy learning.
